glade3: glade3 (User Interface Designer for GTK+ and GNOME)
glade3:
glade3: glade3 is a RAD tool to enable quick & easy development of user 
glade3: interfaces for the GTK+ toolkit and the GNOME desktop environment, 
glade3: released under the GNU GPL License. The user interfaces designed in 
glade3: glade3 are saved as XML, and by using the libglade library these can be 
glade3: loaded by applications dynamically as needed. By using libglade, glade
glade3: XML files can be used in numerous programming languages including C, C++, 
glade3: Java, Perl, Python, C#, Pike, Ruby, Haskell, Objective Caml and Scheme.
glade3:
